text: Sybra postscutellaremaculata is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Breuning in 1964.BioLib.cz - Sybra postscutellaremaculata. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== postscutellaremaculata Category:Beetles described in 1964
